# Test runtime dir (UDS sockets for agentd tests)
# Pin the host sandbox to <worktree>/tmp/uds/ to allow the 4 UDS tests
# in crates/agentd/tests/{control_server,control_client}.rs to run
# locally. Keep the path SHORT — UDS has a ~108 byte path limit (SUN_LEN),
# and our worktree path is already long.
/tmp/
